metadata.name: NFT collector Gennadiy
metadata.description:
Gennadiy. 38 years old. Lives in Russian village with his mom but marks San Francisco in twitter. He likes hentai and macdonalds food.
/
"Drop your NFT I'm buying." These tweets are always very popular. Hundreds of artists are liking, retweeting and sharing their art in hopes of selling it to a generous millionaire. But is this rich owner of BAYC from Twitter real?
 In the "collection of NFT collectors" I will show you with a share of irony and humor who is hiding under the popular shilling requests
/
